[normal]Current[bold] position[bold]:[bold] I am Professor of Forensic Genetics at the Norwegian Institute of Public health and the University of Oslo, Norway.  Previously, I was principle research scientist at the FSS research laboratories for a period of 25 years (1982-2008).
[normal]C.V.is available at: 
[normal]https://sites.google.com/site/peterdgill/
