[normal]Research interests:[bold] 
[normal]1)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]I work primarily on the interpretation and statistics of DNA profiling evidence. I specialise in supporting the development of open-source software to interpret complex mixtures see: 
[normal]http://forensim.r-forge.r-project.org/
[normal] . In addition, current interests include writing a major review, based on recent incidents, on the causes of Miscarriages of Justice. See my website for details of current activities, latest publications and information on training courses: 
[normal]https://sites.google.com/site/forensicdnastatistics/
